title: DAZ3D - POSER - Sci-fi Rover: Titan
description:
Sci-fi rover "Titan" is a large planetary rover for planetary exploration. It is a robust large vehicle capable of operating in conditions of high atmospheric pressure, sandstorms, and the body is built to accommodate uneven terrain. Planetary rover has armor hull and can pull up to eight trailers.

The kit includes two color variants (white/yellow) and three poses for Michael 4 and Genesis 3 . Go out and Explore!
